        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="product-family">
        <div class="product">
            <div class="family-thumbnail text-center">
                <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Cheesecake">Erika</a>
                <img src="../images/Erika.jpg" alt="Cakes" />
            </div>
            <div class="product-description">
                <p><span style="color: #DDC67E;">INTRO: </span></p>
                <p>
                    Erika Valle-Baird here. I got my undergraduate degrees  <br/>
