                     I currently work at Boeing in Washington.  <br />
                </p>
                
                <p><span style="color: #DDC67E;">HOBBIES: </span></p>
                <p>
                    Working out, Sewing, and Playing VR
                </p>
                <p><span style="color: #DDC67E;">FUN FACT: </span></p>
                <p>
                    I taught myself to sew and have become very good at it!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="product-family">
        <div class="product">
            <div class="family-thumbnail text-center">
                <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Cheesecake">Tom</a>
                <img src="../images/Tom.jpeg" alt="Cakes" />
            </div>
            <div class="product-description">
                <p><span style="color: #DDC67E;">INTRO: </span> </p>
                <p>
                     Hello everyone, nice to meet you. I am originally from Michigan, <br/>
